The paper discusses a novel regularization method for compressive imaging in the context of compressed sensing with coherent redundant dictionaries. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also includes simulations and experiments, which fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and signal processing (cs.SI).
